# Expense Management Backend

This is a simple backend project made with **Spring Boot** and **MySQL**.  
It helps you manage users and their expenses easily.

---

## ‚úÖ What You Can Do

- Add a new expense  
- Withdraw an expense  
- Update an expense  
- Delete an expense  
- Add user information  
- Update user information  
- Delete user information  
- Get user information  

---

